languages.text: "Дай мне сил, благослови величием! Лишь прошепчи, какую жертву желаешь..."
"Grant me power! Bless me with glory! Whisper to me whatever sacrifice I must give, and I will offer it gladly..."

languages.text: 「どうか私に力を！栄光の祝福を私に！受けるべき犠牲をお囁きください。何であれ、喜んで差し出します…」
languages.original_text: "Grant me power! Bless me with glory! Whisper to me whatever sacrifice I must give, and I will offer it gladly..."

traits.locale_text: 「どうか私に力を！栄光の祝福を私に！受けるべき犠牲をお囁きください。何であれ、喜んで差し出します…」

languages.text: “赐予我力量吧！赋予我荣耀吧！请您对我耳语吧，无论要我付出怎样的牺牲，我都愿意双手奉上……”
languages.original_text: "Grant me power! Bless me with glory! Whisper to me whatever sacrifice I must give, and I will offer it gladly..."

languages.text: "Schenkt mir Kraft! Segnet mich mit Glanz! Flüstert mir zu, was ich opfern muss, und ich biete es Euch bereitwillig dar ..."
